-- Sony Says Playstation Phone Report in Asahi Newspaper Is `Speculation'
-- B y   Y o s h i n o r i   E k i
-- 2010-12-28T00:12:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-28/sony-calls-playstation-phone-report-in-asahi-newspaper-speculation-.html
Sony Corp. spokesman Atsuo Omagari
declined to comment on an Asahi newspaper report that the
Japanese electronics maker may start sales this spring of a PSP
handheld game machine equipped with a phone. The report is
“speculation,” Omagari said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Yoshinori Eki in Tokyo at 
 yeki@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
